        <text id="2019021208e7d22a35414c1a90000002">
          <inserted>592 <by role="member" id="4841">Mr PICTON (Kaurna)</by> (13 February 2018).  Will the Minister advise what action has been taken to address the crisis of mental health patients causing ambulance ramping at The QEH and other metro hospitals?</inserted>
        </text>
      </talker>
      <talker role="member" id="4342" kind="answer">
